~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : motd                                      ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : motd

   This allows you to view the announcement file, that is shown as 
   you login.  For most people, it scrolls by too fast to read, so 
   this command was added to allow you to see it all.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
